{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9fc027fa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最近、周りのリリアン達に比べ力不足を感じ始めていたコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "676be001",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "リリアンとして今以上に強くなりたい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b66c86e2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──しかし。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f20f7579",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（うう……いざそういうことをって思うと……は、恥ずかしい……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.2",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f20f7579",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "で、でもこれからもあいつと旅をしていくためには、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.4",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "f20f7579",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今以上に強くならないと……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2b0b608f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（それにまったくしらない男の人にされるわけじゃない……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.2",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2b0b608f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "子供の頃から知っているあいつになら……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "57b5ebe3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルはさらに決意を固めるように、自分の頬を軽く叩く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86f71691",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──トントン",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4c8f061d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そろそろ寝ようか、そう思っているとドアのノック音が耳に入る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "47.0",
      "line_index": 47,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dc283488",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "誰だろう……開いてるよ～。勝手に入って～",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.0",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e36ec47",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そうドアの外の人物に声を掛けると、よく見知った幼馴染が入ってきた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e08c31ff",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "よかった……まだ起きていたのね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.0",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "791f127a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ、もう寝ようかなって思っていたんだけど、何か用事か？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.0",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b0d07db7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん……その、た、単刀直入に言うけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8f67cf8f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5828e355",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "普段のコハルとは違い、どこか弱気な印象に少し戸惑う。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61b1cc4b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして小さく頷くと、じっと俺の目を見つめ口を開く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ce5c9fe4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あたしと……え、えっち、して欲しい……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "18bc43b6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──はぁ？　え？　え……何？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.0",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a17909ab",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "えっちよ、えっち！　えっちして欲しいって言ったのっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "90.0",
      "line_index": 90,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "83d72748",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幼馴染の口から今まで出たことの無かった言葉に、思わず固まってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "71df4f67",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ちょっと！　な、何いきなりぼーっとして……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ca61b85d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……その、す、すまん……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.2",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ca61b85d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "なんか突然すごいこと言われてフリーズしてしまって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b12619f5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でもなんでいきなりそんなこと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a8497d1e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルにエッチして欲しいと言われ、全身が一気に熱を帯びる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "980493ea",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "額から汗がにじみ出し、顔が赤くなってしまっているのが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.2",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "980493ea",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "自分でもわかってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b10b6c17",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしそれはコハルも同様で、頬が紅く染まり、照れくさいのか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.2",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b10b6c17",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "伏し目がちにチラチラと俺をみつめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.0",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c99a23f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "初めて見るコハルのそんな表情に、ドキドキと胸が高鳴り、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "108.2",
      "line_index": 108,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c99a23f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ヘンに現実感が無いような気がしてきてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37ea64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その……あ、あんたほかの子と……し、しているんでしょ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.2",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "37ea64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それで最近ほかの子がどんどん力を伸ばして……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.0",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75aeee1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからあたしもって……そ、そう思って……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "719122ec",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ば、ばか！　だからって、そんな簡単にするもんじゃないだろっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.0",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c28f0c7b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "確かに彼女たちは俺と関係を持つと力が強くなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.0",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f0a813d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからと言って、それだけが目的で関係を持ったわけじゃない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.0",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c9367f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな思いから思わずコハルに怒ってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c420f933",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "じゃあなんでほかの子にはしてあたしにはダメなのよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "46afaf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そ、それは……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.2",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "46afaf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その、ふ、雰囲気に流されてというか……そ、そんな感じで……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c7dfb032",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だったらいいじゃない！　あたしに流される感じでも！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "276dc94e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でもコハルには……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "276dc94e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うう、そういうことで関係を持ちたくないっていうか…… ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.4",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "276dc94e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その、上手く言えないけど、大事にしたいっていうか……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1921bbd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、あたしだって……その、あんたじゃなければこんなこと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.2",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1921bbd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "い、言ったりなんて……あんただから……あたし……うぅぅ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.0",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9711980c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは瞳にうっすらと涙を浮かべながら、じっと俺をみつめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "452f8b27",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなコハルに申し訳なさが溢れ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.2",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "452f8b27",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わずコハルの小さな身体を抱きしめてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.0",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8912d775",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたいつの間にこんなに大きい身体になったのよ……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "153.2",
      "line_index": 153,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8912d775",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少し前まであたしと全然かわらなかったのに……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "156.0",
      "line_index": 156,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "396c1f1f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "大人……になったからな。でもそれはコハルも同じなんだよな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6863c311",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん……あんたとあたしは男と女になったんだよ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.2",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6863c311",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからお願い……あたしと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "176.0",
      "line_index": 176,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "399ec26f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "きゃうっ！♥　あ、あ……手……入って……ううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aff76827",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルのパンツに手を突っ込み、割れ目をそっと撫でる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb393d45",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の指の動きにビクンと身体を跳ねらせ反応するコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d061aff2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すでにあそこはべっとりと濡れており、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.2",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d061aff2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルが俺を求めていてくれたことに喜びを覚える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61b8521",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もうあそこぐっしょりだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.2",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "61b8521",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルって真面目一筋だと思っていたけど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.4",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "61b8521",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "案外エッチなやつだったんだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.0",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a7e47b00",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、うるさい～……そんなこと言わないでよぉ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "81b17554",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の言葉に恥ずかしそうに声をあげるコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "192.0",
      "line_index": 192,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "af947c2d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "普段のコハルからは想像もできない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "192.2",
      "line_index": 192,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "af947c2d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "小動物のような仕草にギャップを感じ、さらに胸がドキドキしてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.0",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3cad3be5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたの心臓の音……はっきり伝わってくる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "195.2",
      "line_index": 195,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3cad3be5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたもドキドキしているんだね……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "69766f18",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、当たり前だろっ。コハルにドキドキしないわけないって",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "207.0",
      "line_index": 207,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2e184f87",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あっ！♥　あぁっ！♥　い、いきなりそんな……んんんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.0",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b111a774",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルに自分の胸の高鳴りを聞かれ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.2",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b111a774",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "妙な恥ずかしさと照れくささを感じてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.0",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2940125",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "照れ隠しをするように割れ目を沿うように指を動かすと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.2",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2940125",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは全身を震わせ、刺激に足をぴくぴくと震わせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "214.0",
      "line_index": 214,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3e069ae2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だ、めぇ♥　そんな激しく……あうっ！♥　ふあ、ああっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.0",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7d5c860b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "愛撫の快感に脚を閉じようとするコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "217.0",
      "line_index": 217,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "df8aea74",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それを阻止するように両脚でコハルの脚をがっちりと固定させる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "219.0",
      "line_index": 219,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87aa0ab3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "無防備になってしまっているあそこを",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "219.2",
      "line_index": 219,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "87aa0ab3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "執拗に指でなぞり続けると、膣穴からさらに大量の愛液が溢れ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "219.4",
      "line_index": 219,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "87aa0ab3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "くちゅくちゅと水音が大きくなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.0",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2be1c9f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、あっ！♥　これ、すごい……んんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.2",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2be1c9f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "じ、自分の指と大違い……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.0",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "808d114d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたにされるのがこんなにも気持ち良いなんてぇ♥　んんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "228.0",
      "line_index": 228,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42656490",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いつもは一人でしているのか？やっぱりコハルはエッチなんだな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.0",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34d23c85",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うるさいぃぃっ！♥　んぅ！♥　だって大好きなんだもんっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.2",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "34d23c85",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたのこと考えると、おまんこ疼いて",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.4",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "34d23c85",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぐちゅぐちゅになっちゃうんだもんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "235.0",
      "line_index": 235,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aeb54205",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ずっとずっとこうして欲しいって……思っていたんだからぁ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.0",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "795bcb74",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハル……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "241.0",
      "line_index": 241,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "95aeff5f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは顔を真っ赤にしながら、赤裸々に俺への想いを伝えてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "243.0",
      "line_index": 243,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "396a7d1b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなコハルに愛しさを覚え、もうオナニーはさせない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "243.2",
      "line_index": 243,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "396a7d1b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺がいくらでもコハルを満足させる、そんな思いが芽生えてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "246.0",
      "line_index": 246,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a0b08711",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃっ！♥　指、あそこにぃ……あぁっ！♥　んあああっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.0",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9c8deadc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ヒクヒクと蠢く膣穴に指を差し込むと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.2",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9c8deadc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "待ちわびていたようにするりと飲み込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "250.0",
      "line_index": 250,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8eebcbec",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "中の愛液を掻き出すように指を動かすと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "250.2",
      "line_index": 250,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8eebcbec",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの甘い声がさらに大きくなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "250.4",
      "line_index": 250,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "8eebcbec",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "熱を帯びていた小さな身体がさらに熱くなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "253.0",
      "line_index": 253,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bd3667d4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭……ぼーっとしちゃう♥　おまんこ、気持ち良いよぉ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "253.2",
      "line_index": 253,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bd3667d4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "も、もっと……くちゅくちゅして……んんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "256.0",
      "line_index": 256,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4b235171",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたの指であたしをイかせて……お願いぃ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "259.0",
      "line_index": 259,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f00358f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、もちろんイかせるよ。コハルのイクところ見せてくれっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "263.0",
      "line_index": 263,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "163abe7a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひあぁっ！♥　あ、んあああ！♥　ああ、そんな、同時にぃ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "263.2",
      "line_index": 263,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "163abe7a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、んああぁっ！♥　ああ、ふあああぁぁ～～っ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.0",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "56444f50",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "胸とあそこを同時にした経験が無いのか、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "265.2",
      "line_index": 265,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "56444f50",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二重の快感に全身をくねらせるコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "267.0",
      "line_index": 267,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "83064dc7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに強くコハルの身体を抱き、指を大きく強く動かしていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "270.0",
      "line_index": 270,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6538afbd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "これっ！♥　すごすぎぃ！♥　もうダメ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "270.2",
      "line_index": 270,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6538afbd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あたし、イっちゃう！♥　あんたにイかされちゃうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "272.0",
      "line_index": 272,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4a4bb19",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの絶頂の合図に合わせるようにさらに指を一本押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "273.0",
      "line_index": 273,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c7335a12",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして二本の指で膣穴を拡げるように、ぐちゅぐちゅと掻き回していく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "276.0",
      "line_index": 276,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2a41bf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──ひいいっ！？♥　んあっ、あああぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "276.2",
      "line_index": 276,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2a41bf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメっ！♥　ダメ！♥　イク、イクっ♥　おまんこイクっ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.0",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6b4b380d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "イっちゃうぅぅぅっ！♥　んああああぁぁぁ～～っ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "311.0",
      "line_index": 311,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f86a0284",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふあぁっ！♥　あ、ああっ♥　んぅ！♥　ふううううっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "313.0",
      "line_index": 313,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9f0a73dc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一瞬の硬直後、コハルは絶叫と共に全身を大きく震わせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "314.0",
      "line_index": 314,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ecd5d8da",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "膣奥から大量の愛液が溢れ、パンツがぐっしょりとなるほど溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "317.0",
      "line_index": 317,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "452db34b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うう……♥　気持ち、良い～♥　こ、こんなの初めて……はぁぁ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "319.0",
      "line_index": 319,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3c687346",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの全身から力が抜け、ぐったりと俺に寄りかかる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "320.0",
      "line_index": 320,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f6021b60",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肩で大きく呼吸を繰り返し、蕩けた瞳で呆然と天井を見つめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "322.0",
      "line_index": 322,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae95fdd5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あそこから指を引き抜こうとしたとき、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "322.2",
      "line_index": 322,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ae95fdd5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "慌てて俺の腕を掴むコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "325.0",
      "line_index": 325,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6073d537",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ま、待って……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "327.0",
      "line_index": 327,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5bb946f5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "蕩けた声で俺を呼び止める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "329.0",
      "line_index": 329,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a7972602",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その瞳と声からコハルが何故俺の腕を掴んだのかわかってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "330.0",
      "line_index": 330,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e91a8426",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも悪戯心が芽生えてしまい、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "330.2",
      "line_index": 330,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e91a8426",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "とぼけたふりをしてコハルに説明を求める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "333.0",
      "line_index": 333,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9046bd9a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "どうしたんだ？　もうすることはしたし、そろそろ寝ないと",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "337.0",
      "line_index": 337,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91600249",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、うう……♥　その……も、もっとしてよぉ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "339.0",
      "line_index": 339,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c3a46a4b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "甘えた声でおねだりをしてくるコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "340.0",
      "line_index": 340,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "23ebc4c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "初めて聞く幼馴染のそんな声に、思わず胸が高鳴る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "343.0",
      "line_index": 343,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ed596abb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おまんこ……もっとぐちゅぐちゅして……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "343.2",
      "line_index": 343,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ed596abb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたの指でいっぱい犯して……♥　お願い～……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "346.0",
      "line_index": 346,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "def4cce",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああもう、なんて可愛いんだよコハルはっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "349.0",
      "line_index": 349,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6c447aa5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルのあまりの可愛さに、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "349.2",
      "line_index": 349,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6c447aa5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらにぎゅっと身体を抱きしめてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "352.0",
      "line_index": 352,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9747ab55",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "なんかもう色々と頭の中で弾け飛んだかも……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "352.2",
      "line_index": 352,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9747ab55",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっとはげしくするかもしれないけど……いいか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "356.0",
      "line_index": 356,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58348ace",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん♥　全然いいよ♥　あんたにならいくらでもされてもいいの♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "356.2",
      "line_index": 356,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "58348ace",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからもっとおまんこ愛して……♥　ズボズボ犯して……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "364.0",
      "line_index": 364,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "db7e34ee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふぎぃぃっ！♥　うあ、あああっ♥　んあああぁぁぁぁ～っ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "366.0",
      "line_index": 366,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b295eb4c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "興奮に任せコハルのパンツを脱がすと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "366.2",
      "line_index": 366,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b295eb4c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "露になったあそこに指を根元まで押し込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "368.0",
      "line_index": 368,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "318b6343",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "膣中を掻きまわすように指の出し入れを繰り返すと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "368.2",
      "line_index": 368,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "318b6343",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは全身を震わせ、甘い悲鳴を何度も口から漏らす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "371.0",
      "line_index": 371,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c1f57ef1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああぁぁ～っ！♥　あんたの指、いいのぉっ！♥おまんこ蕩けるぅ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "371.2",
      "line_index": 371,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c1f57ef1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "も、もう一人でエッチできなくなっちゃうよぉ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "374.0",
      "line_index": 374,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1365bbdb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう一人でする必要なんてないって。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "374.2",
      "line_index": 374,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1365bbdb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺がいくらでもコハルを満足させてやるからっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "378.0",
      "line_index": 378,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6141b074",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひうううっ！♥　あ、あぁっ！♥　んぅ！♥　んんんんっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "380.0",
      "line_index": 380,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86c8de5c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルはビクンと身体を震わせ、再び絶頂する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.0",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c47206d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "絶頂しているにも関わらず指を動かし続け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.2",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c47206d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そしてぷっくりと大きくなっていた乳首を摘まみ上げ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "381.4",
      "line_index": 381,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "c47206d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに刺激を与えていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "384.0",
      "line_index": 384,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bae6706",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んんんっ！♥　あああっ！♥　ダメ、イクの止まらないぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "384.2",
      "line_index": 384,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bae6706",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んっ！♥　ふ、ふああああーーっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "386.0",
      "line_index": 386,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "32a2a5ba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度も俺の指で絶頂を繰り返すコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "387.0",
      "line_index": 387,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3574e5b1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白に濁った愛液が掻き出され、コハルの下半身をいやらしく濡らす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.0",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2131cad0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの女性の匂いが鼻孔に直撃し、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "389.2",
      "line_index": 389,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2131cad0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その匂いがさらに俺を興奮させていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "392.0",
      "line_index": 392,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "38368b6b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おまんこイキっぱなしぃぃぃっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "392.2",
      "line_index": 392,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "38368b6b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おかしくなっちゃうぅ！♥　はううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "394.0",
      "line_index": 394,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cde0de56",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルのあそこは指をぎゅっと締め付け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "394.2",
      "line_index": 394,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cde0de56",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに膣奥からどろどろの愛液が溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "396.0",
      "line_index": 396,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f648563e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "淫らな水音とコハルの喘ぎ声が混ざり合い、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "396.2",
      "line_index": 396,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f648563e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらにコハルを喜ばせようと、はげしく指の出し入れを繰り返す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "399.0",
      "line_index": 399,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "251ea252",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふううっ！？♥　あ、あ……ちょ、ちょっと……うううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "399.2",
      "line_index": 399,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "251ea252",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "待って……そ、その……う……んぅぅぅぅっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "401.0",
      "line_index": 401,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1a9f5340",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あそこの愛撫を続ていると、急に腰を捩らせ始めるコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "403.0",
      "line_index": 403,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "241637ca",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも俺は指を止めることができず、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "403.2",
      "line_index": 403,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "241637ca",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルを抑えるように抱きしめ、ひたすらに指であそこを愛し続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "406.0",
      "line_index": 406,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "51916299",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメ、ダメぇ！♥　と、止まってぇ……あううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "406.2",
      "line_index": 406,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "51916299",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何か……んぅ、ふ、ふあ……これ……ダメ……！♥　あああっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "408.0",
      "line_index": 408,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "12b6d385",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今までとは明らかに違う反応を見せるコハル。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "409.0",
      "line_index": 409,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "afb9f99b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "恥ずかしそうに頬を紅く染め、腰をぶるぶると震わせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "412.0",
      "line_index": 412,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "44f9aabe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメっ♥　ダメダメっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "412.2",
      "line_index": 412,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "44f9aabe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こ、これ……で、出ちゃう……！♥　やめて……出ちゃうのぉっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "412.4",
      "line_index": 412,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "44f9aabe",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、あぁっ！　んんぅぅぅっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "415.0",
      "line_index": 415,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fe11b310",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あっ……！♥　も、もう……う、ううぅっ、んんんんんんっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "446.0",
      "line_index": 446,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21c76a64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふううううっ！♥　んぅぅぅ！♥　んんんんんーーーっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "448.0",
      "line_index": 448,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8cec76f1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルのイク声と共に、大量の潮が噴き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "450.0",
      "line_index": 450,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e3b1e10f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "潮を噴くほど俺の指でコハルが感じた……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "451.0",
      "line_index": 451,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3f339fd2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それがさらに俺を高ぶらせ、潮吹きをしているにも関わらず愛撫を続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "454.0",
      "line_index": 454,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8b28260f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んひぃぃっ！♥　うう、なに、これぇ……あううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "454.2",
      "line_index": 454,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8b28260f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お漏らし、とまらにゃいぃぃぃ♥　はうううぅ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "457.0",
      "line_index": 457,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d6ddbf93",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "出るの……気持ち良いよぉ♥　ふあ、あ、あああぁぁぁっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "459.0",
      "line_index": 459,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b1c1fc63",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは瞳に涙を浮かべながら、さらに絶頂を繰り返す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "461.0",
      "line_index": 461,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4f7b58d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう何度コハルを絶頂させたかわからない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "461.2",
      "line_index": 461,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4f7b58d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも俺もコハルも満足できずひたすらにあそこに愛撫を続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "464.0",
      "line_index": 464,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8d6c33f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふぅ、ふぅぅっ♥　もっと、もっとおまんこ……くちゅくちゅして♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "464.2",
      "line_index": 464,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8d6c33f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっとお漏らしさせて……♥　いっぱいイかせて……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "467.0",
      "line_index": 467,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "278528b5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ、コハルが心の底から満足するまで付き合うから。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "467.2",
      "line_index": 467,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "278528b5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だからコハルの誰にも見せたことのない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "467.4",
      "line_index": 467,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "278528b5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一番エッチで可愛い姿をもっと見せてくれ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "471.0",
      "line_index": 471,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53e09bfd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん……♥　いっぱい見て……んんんっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "471.2",
      "line_index": 471,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "53e09bfd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あたし以外の子が見えなくなるくらいエッチなあたしを見続けて♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "474.0",
      "line_index": 474,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a47ebab0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あんたの心があたしでいっぱいになるまでイかせてぇ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "476.0",
      "line_index": 476,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "173f7a44",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらにぐちゅぐちゅとコハルのあそこに手淫を続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "477.0",
      "line_index": 477,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9c7fee0e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それはコハルがイキ続け、気を失うまで続くのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
